Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 1042 "Police Academy \NArc Wild Police Story CASE. Hagiwara Kenji"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,[ed]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:05.97,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Between six to ten months \Nat the police academy,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.68,0:00:11.19,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,students receive education and \Ntraining to become police officers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:17.49,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,and establish deeper bonds with friends as \Nthey become fully-fledged police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:23.50,Nonbei,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Nonbei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:23.28,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.37,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this started.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.75,0:00:27.71,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.52,0:00:36.59,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Man, nothing beats free beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:36.59,Date,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,460)}Date Wataru (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.36,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by free beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.77,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Hagiwara didn't tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.07,0:00:45.77,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He said he'd pay for our drinks \Nif we attended this mixer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.77,0:00:49.77,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,with girls from another class \Nso there'd be enough guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.82,Matsuda,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,460)}Matsuda Jinpei (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:54.78,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}And that's why you're here even \Nthough you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:01:00.45,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Hagiwara himself still \Nhasn't arrived, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:03.73,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,What? Date-kun, you have a girlfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.73,0:01:06.63,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you can tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.63,0:01:07.72,DCMain,WATARU,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:09.41,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Matsuda-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:10.41,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.41,0:01:12.55,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You don't, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:14.13,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.80,0:01:20.97,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hey, Hiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:24.60,Furuya,SIGN LEFT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,460)}Furuya Rei (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:24.60,Morofushi,SIGN RIGHT,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,460)}Morofushi Hiromitsu (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.97,0:01:23.61,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This appetizer is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:27.90,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Even I could make this. \NI'll show you how sometime.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.38,0:01:30.47,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you don't know the \Nfirst thing about cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.19,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:35.24,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Morofushi-kun, teach me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.24,0:01:38.07,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,I just want Furuya-kun to cook \Nfor me, even if he sucks at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:39.55,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:43.33,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Zero's interest in women other \Nthan older lady doctors is zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.02,0:01:48.82,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda-kun, keep saying unkind things...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.09,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll arrest you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.46,0:01:53.71,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.22,0:01:56.80,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Nice punch, right, Zero?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.63,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.01,0:02:08.89,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:12.77,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.77,Hagiwara,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Hagiwara Kenji (22)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:17.95,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,There was an old woman stuck on \Nthe long steps on the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:19.66,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,After carrying her up the steps,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:24.29,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,she said she dropped the very lucky \Nfortune she just got at the shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:26.86,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,We tried looking for it, but couldn't find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:31.35,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,so we went back to the shrine to buy \Nfortunes until we got another very lucky one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.54,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,and that brings us to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:35.24,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.55,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.74,0:02:38.80,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,You're so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.26,0:02:40.36,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.34,0:02:44.88,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,That was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:47.43,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've had too much to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:51.06,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go karaoke next?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.94,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.14,0:02:55.77,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.69,0:02:58.09,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.70,0:03:02.54,DCMain,GIRL,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.61,0:03:04.18,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Like I expected, Hagi's \Ngetting all the attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.74,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.69,0:03:08.91,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.53,0:03:13.13,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that tall man over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:14.58,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.58,0:03:19.61,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did he carry me earlier, \Nhe even bought me some fortunes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.61,0:03:22.49,DCMain,MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Could you thank him for me, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:23.58,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.34,0:03:26.60,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,So it was true after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:29.06,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hagi doesn't lie about that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.67,0:03:33.13,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Although he probably called the \Nold dude he helped an old lady
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.13,0:03:35.06,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,because he knew it would be received better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.40,0:04:01.99,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What's wrong, Hiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.81,0:04:04.34,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.32,0:04:07.31,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.91,0:04:10.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,It comes to visit after falling asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.46,0:04:12.46,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Fall in love with logical deduction \Nand the pleasure of solving mysteries!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:14.30,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Their passionate youth known \Nonly by their classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.30,0:04:16.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Cherry blossoms that don't fall are forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.48,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.48,0:04:19.23,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:21.74,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:09.93,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)}Police Academy Arc Wild Police \NStory CASE. Hagiwara Kenji
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:09.29,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Police Academy Arc Wild Police \NStory CASE. Hagiwara Kenji."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.78,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,My throat hurts from singing \Ntoo much at karaoke yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.78,0:06:23.27,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.82,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It was the Hagiwara show at karaoke, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.21,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,How cool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:45.12,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, that's an RX-7 FD3S.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.71,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Who's driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.22,Onizuka,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,1)}Onizuka Hachizo (48) \NRookie Class Instructor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:53.29,DCItalic,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,It's Instructor Oni's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:57.87,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,That's your car, Instructor Onizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:06:59.81,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,This is no ordinary car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:03.06,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,In some ways, this baby's a fighter plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.27,0:07:09.83,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Its lightweight body was inspired \Nby the Zero fighter plane, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.83,0:07:13.07,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,The spirit of the Zero lives \Non in that incredible car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.61,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed, Instructor Onizuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:19.60,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,You drive my favorite car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:23.83,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, it's not my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:27.59,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,It belonged to one of my \Nseniors who died on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:31.82,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Four years ago, his daughter declared to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.82,0:07:35.71,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,that she'd become a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.71,0:07:37.85,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm holding onto it until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.28,0:07:40.60,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Park it in the garage for me, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.95,0:07:43.05,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not scratch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.23,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:47.68,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe that guy's daughter is cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:52.21,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,She wants to be a cop. She's \Nprobably a stubborn tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.69,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Zero, do you feel like \Ngoing for a ride now, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.30,0:08:08.07,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're both zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:13.14,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. I'm not into flashy cars like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.39,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,So that is what you're into.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.89,EquipTraining,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(375,1)}Heavy Equipment Training
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:20.10,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, one more lap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:22.39,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Quit lollygagging and pick up the pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.30,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:30.22,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Your family runs an auto \Nrepair shop, Hagiwara?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.22,0:08:33.15,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you knew so much about the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:38.16,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. Jinpei-chan used to come to \Nour shop all the time as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:43.29,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,He got in trouble with my dad for disassembling\N and modding stuff without permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:47.21,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I was just trying to install \Ngull wings on a Porsche.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.21,DCItalic,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,That would make anyone angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.55,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just cars either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.55,0:08:55.03,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,By the end, he was researching explosives.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.03,0:08:57.97,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can mostly tell how one's \Nbuilt just by looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.48,0:09:05.03,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Since I like tinkering, too, \NI wanted to take over the shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.73,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you decide to \Nbecome a police officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:13.11,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Just as business was going well and we \Nwere increasing the number of shops,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:15.75,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,the economy suddenly collapsed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:19.12,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's shop ended up going bankrupt.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:25.50,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, the police will \Nnever go out of business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.31,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.31,0:09:29.50,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.14,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,You've got half a lap left!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.76,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,Show some spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.89,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go for a last spurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.20,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:52.82,MotoTraining,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Motorcycle Skill Training
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.49,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:59.02,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like your carburetor's \Nnot regulating fuel properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:01.58,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so, too, and was about to fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.81,0:10:09.26,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not as fast as you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.31,0:10:11.59,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,See? All better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:14.55,DCMain,SUNGLASSES,0000,0000,0000,,You're as dexterous as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:17.97,DCMain,SUNGLASSES,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda Jinpei and Hagiwara Kenji.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:21.42,DCMain,SUNGLASSES,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any interest in the riot police?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.57,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.57,0:10:26.77,DCMain,SUNGLASSES,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, I'd like to \Nscout you for the bomb squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.77,0:10:30.14,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,The riot police bomb squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:34.11,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm obviously interested!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:37.11,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for reaching out to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.39,0:10:39.82,DCItalic,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't sound like a thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.95,DCMain,SUNGLASSES,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh... What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.29,0:10:48.15,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:50.83,Nameplate,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Morofushi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:55.59,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Hiro, I'm going out. Want me \Nto pick anything up for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.25,0:10:59.78,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Did Hiro go out somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:21.53,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna tell him, Hagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:26.79,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently they think we'd immediately \Nbe useful members of the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:32.14,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to be on the same \Nsquad as an old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.14,0:11:35.21,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but I'd get to \Ntinker, which I love to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:37.13,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.48,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,My dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:42.22,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Because I saw what happened to my dad's shop,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:46.25,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,when everything's going \Nwell, I step on the brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.24,0:11:52.73,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help but wonder if \Nthese are the gates to ruin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.48,Lounge,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,Lounge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.51,0:11:56.08,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not sure about \Nit, then don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.83,0:12:02.26,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb squad is pretty serious business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.50,0:12:06.74,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to eat, I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.94,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check out Instructor Oni's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:14.42,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,When I told him I could tell what part \Nof a machine is broken from the sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:16.75,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,he asked me to check out the car's engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:20.01,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,He asked to wash it while I was at it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.45,0:12:24.60,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out of here and into \Nthe bomb squad fast enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.08,0:12:28.15,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.38,0:12:33.89,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,The bomb squad doesn't scare you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.49,0:12:38.15,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be lying if I said it didn't scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.58,0:12:42.90,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,But I've been interested in \Nthe bomb squad for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.85,0:12:45.41,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,and besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:51.91,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all gas, no brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:56.42,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.13,0:13:19.31,DCItalic,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of bike shops, I saw a guy \Nwith a strange tattoo the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.48,DCItalic,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Like a cup with a fancy base.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:22.94,DCItalic,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's called a goblet?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:31.83,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I followed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:35.56,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You had an unusual look on \Nyour face when you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:37.21,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,T-Team Leader Date.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:40.77,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you \Ncame here to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:43.86,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,but if you don't want to tell \Nme, then you don't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:45.75,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just be watching you \Nfrom right next to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.75,0:13:47.22,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I won't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:51.68,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,I might occasionally talk to myself though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.48,0:13:56.06,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give up, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:14:00.25,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I can't give out my \Ncustomers' personal information.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.25,0:14:04.86,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I just need you to arrange a meeting \Nwith the man with the goblet tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:06.16,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.16,0:14:08.86,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about Irie-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:10.53,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:13.54,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You're the cleaner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:16.38,DCMain,CLERK,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Tomori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:20.17,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. These guys are \Ntrying to become police officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.78,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,They helped some people at a \Nconvenience store the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:24.55,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:28.35,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What is this Irie person like?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.29,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,He's a quiet hardware salesman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.29,0:14:34.56,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,He joined us on the neighborhood \Nassociation's trip to the hot springs the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:37.17,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:40.30,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Irie-san doesn't like photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:45.82,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Normally you'd take group photos \Non a group trip like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.04,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mentioned it, we did take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.49,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.89,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.89,0:14:55.99,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,This guy in the black tank top is Irie-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.85,0:15:02.44,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,But why are you looking \Nfor a man with a tattoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.44,0:15:06.00,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,These days there are plenty \Nof people with tattoos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.61,0:15:11.26,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,There's a scorpion tattoo on \Nthe back of this clerk's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:15.40,DCMain,TOMORI,0000,0000,0000,,And I've got the goddess \NKannon on my upper arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:21.94,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,No, the tattoo I saw years ago was \Na goblet on someone's shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.69,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:34.46,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check out the driver seat of the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.46,0:15:36.33,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Hey, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:40.53,DCMain,OLD WOMAN,0000,0000,0000,,We hit the gas instead of the \Nbrakes and crashed into the truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.53,0:15:43.46,DCMain,OLD MAN,0000,0000,0000,,Now our bumper is stuck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.91,0:15:46.96,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,And the truck drove off \Nwithout noticing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:51.01,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. There's a car stuck \Nto the back of your truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.58,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good, team leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.58,0:15:57.10,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,The driver is unconscious \Nbecause he's sick or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:59.48,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it. He's accelerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.85,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,He must've lost consciousness \Nwith his foot on the gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:03.73,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I need to call someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:07.83,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Zero say he was going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:13.96,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What? A runaway truck has a \Ncar stuck to its rear bumper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.49,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Is the truck driver unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:20.25,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. He's currently \Nspeeding towards Hachioji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.73,0:16:24.94,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Team Leader Date and I are following him on \Na bike we borrowed from a soba restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.94,0:16:27.25,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Please clear the road ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:30.01,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,This is a runaway truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.58,0:16:33.44,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It's all we can do to use \Nthe bullhorn we borrowed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:36.14,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,from someone making a campaign \Nspeech to clear the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:39.16,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Have you called the police \Nand fire departments?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.16,0:16:42.64,DCItalic,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but you're closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:44.99,DCItalic,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Clear the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:45.65,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,You'd get here quicker \Nin the instructor's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:47.86,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What? The instructor's car?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.86,0:16:50.65,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Jinpei-chan's checking out the FD right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.49,0:16:53.65,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:57.91,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. He should be \Nrepairing or washing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.71,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:11.25,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,It's barely driving straight ahead \Nwhile scraping against the guardrail,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.64,0:17:13.80,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,but at this rate, sooner or later...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.31,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, team leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.45,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.19,0:17:24.49,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:27.62,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,We're forbidden from driving \Nvehicles like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.62,0:17:28.52,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:31.07,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I can't hear you over \Nthe sound of the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.69,0:17:34.08,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,We need to do something to stop that truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.08,0:17:36.57,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:40.99,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Ramming it will physically force it to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:49.04,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,It's not working. The difference \Nin weight is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.74,0:17:57.30,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hagiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.52,0:18:02.43,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Think you can do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:04.85,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.60,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:10.68,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, open your sunroof!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.68,0:18:11.98,DCMain,OLD MAN,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.76,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.56,0:18:15.49,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.24,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bite your tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.24,0:18:22.24,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.61,0:18:26.13,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,A passenger car's bumper got stuck \Nwhen it crashed into a truck
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.00,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,and is now being dragged along behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:32.02,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but something caused the \Ntruck driver to lose consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:36.02,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do \Nunder these circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.02,0:18:40.43,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.04,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:11.54,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Open the hood when we get \Nto the front of the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:17.02,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'll remove the bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:18.80,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,You get the truck driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.38,0:19:20.31,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:28.02,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Team leader, this road isn't on the GPS.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.20,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,It might be an under-construction highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.20,0:19:33.98,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, this road comes to a sudden end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:38.07,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I removed all the clips \Non the inside of the bumper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.60,0:19:41.82,DCMain,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,Pull the handbrake as hard as \Nyou can and rip the bumper off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:51.16,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Furuya-chan, hurry. \NYou're running out of road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:54.00,DCItalic,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he slams on the brakes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.00,0:19:57.23,DCItalic,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,it takes a ten-ton truck \Nroughly twice the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.23,0:19:59.17,DCItalic,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,of a passenger car to \Ncome to a complete stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:02.47,DCItalic,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he brakes now, \Nhe won't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.64,0:20:17.84,DCItalic,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.98,DCItalic,MATSUDA,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all gas, no brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:25.34,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,The gas! You have to step on the gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:28.49,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Step on it, Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.59,0:20:42.77,DCMain,DATE,0000,0000,0000,,Crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.30,0:20:44.13,DCMain,MOROFUSHI,0000,0000,0000,,He's not making it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:04.06,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.62,0:21:05.60,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.10,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Your advice was perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:28.59,DCMain,FURUYA,0000,0000,0000,,Without it, I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.83,0:21:31.21,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:35.68,DCMain,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that's what he would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.89,0:21:43.82,DCItalic,HAGIWARA,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe stepping on the gas every once \Nin a while isn't such a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:13.37,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, I haven't been \Nfilled in on the details yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:16.37,DCMain,ONIZUKA,0000,0000,0000,,but I heard you helped rescue some people.
